{"id": 243227592, "title": "Adult film star Austin Wolf arrested for allegedly receiving, distributing child pornography", "text": "Adult film star Austin Wolf has been arrested on charges of child pornography. The Department of Justice announced the news Friday, saying that Wolf \u2014 legal name: Justin Heath Smith \u2014 has been charged with receiving and sending \u201chundreds of videos\u201d of child porn using an anonymous account via the Telegram app. \u201cThose videos depicted children as young as infants, including a video showing a 10-year-old child bound and raped,\u201d the DOJ said, calling that specific video \u201cghastly.\u201d The DOJ added that Smith, 43, has also been charged with \u201cpossessing hundreds of additional videos containing child pornography in his Manhattan apartment.\u201d According to the allegations contained in the criminal complaint, Smith\u2019s alleged activity took place over the course of a mere five days in March. At that point, the FBI \u201cseized and searched\u201d the phone of the individual with whom Smith had allegedly been communicating. \u201cAn undercover FBI agent subsequently began a conversation with Smith\u2019s anonymous Telegram account,\u201d the complaint said. \u201cIn the course of those conversations, Smith revealed details that confirmed his identity.\u201d In April, the FBI executed a search warrant at Smith\u2019s Manhattan apartment, where agents discovered \u201can SD card with hundreds of videos containing child pornography.\u201d Smith has been charged with one count of distribution and receipt of child pornography, and one count of possession of child pornography. The former carries a mandatory minimum sentence of five years in prison and a maximum sentence of 20 years in prison, while the latter carries a maximum sentence of 10 years in prison. Reps for Smith did not immediately respond to Page Six\u2019s request for comment. Anyone with information about Smith\u2019s alleged conduct is encouraged to call the FBI at 1-800-CALL-FBI.", "summary": "According to the allegations contained in the criminal complaint, his alleged activity took place over the course of a mere five days in March.", "url": "https://pagesix.com/2024/06/28/celebrity-news/adult-film-star-austin-wolf-arrested-on-child-pornography-charges/", "image": "https://pagesix.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/06/84641647.jpg?quality=75&strip=all&w=1200", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-29 00:46:07", "author": "Bernie Zilio", "authors": ["Bernie Zilio"], "language": "en", "source_country": "us", "sentiment": -0.156}